OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 1 JUN
OL,4,G1540FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GPeterborough. Rosie has ruffled
OL,6,     Gfeathers all week. Now it's her
OL,7,     Gguests' turn to scour every
OL,8,     Gelement of her Brazilian night,
OL,9,     Gfrom the samba dancers to her
OL,10,     Gauthentic pig-ear stew.
OL,11,G1615FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe competition kicks off at
OL,13,     GAnstey Hall in Cambridge, where
OL,14,     Gfather and son John and Johnny de
OL,15,     GBruyne hope to impress their
OL,16,     Gguests with an afternoon of goose
OL,17,     Gherding and a formal dinner.
