OL,4,G1650FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe second visit is to the
OL,6,     Gclothes-free Clover Spa and Hotel
OL,7,     Gin Birmingham, where owner Tim
OL,8,     GHiggs plans to convert his rivals
OL,9,     Gto the joys of naturism.
OL,10,G1720FFour in a Bed
OL,11,     GMark Davidson and Layla Caton are
OL,12,     Gdetermined to deliver a heavenly
OL,13,     Gstay at The Angel Hotel in
OL,14,     GColeford, Gloucestershire. But
OL,15,     Gmanners slip over dinner and
OL,16,     Gthere's confusion at breakfast.
OL,17,G1750FFour in a Bed
OL,18,     GThe final visit is to Higher
OL,19,     GGitcombe in Totnes, Devon, run by
OL,20,     GLynnie and Paul Jolly. But not
OL,21,     Geveryone is impressed by their
OL,22,     Gefforts to spoil their guests.
