OL,4,G1820FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GOn the last day of the
OL,6,     Gcompetition, the B&Bers tackle
OL,7,     Gnegative feedback about self-
OL,8,     Gservice breakfast and an indecent
OL,9,     Gfind, before the payments are
OL,10,     Grevealed and the winner is
OL,11,     Gannounced.
OL,12,G1850FLocation, Location, Location
OL,13,     GKirstie Allsopp and Phil Spencer
OL,14,     Ghouse-hunt in London the week
OL,15,     Gafter the Brexit vote. Sisters
OL,16,     GRuth and Anna pool their funds,
OL,17,     Gwhile Aba has champagne tastes
OL,18,     Gbut lemonade money.
